{"tid":2238920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★百佳現金券---保良局、仁愛堂、惜食堂、香港傷殘青年協會、循道衞理 只派發予會員！政黨接過百投訴","createTime":"2020-10-11T13:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T12:52:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa642a63b56fd9a6239a814e888471f5cb1f83e","tid":2238920,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:32:29.000Z","msg":"27間社福機構九龍西的辦事處或服務點以電話查詢領取詳情，包括<span class=\"xx-large\">保良局、仁愛堂、惜食堂、香港傷殘青年協會、循道衞理楊震社會服務處等</span>，結果所有機構均以非會員為由拒絕申請，回覆包括「不對外派發，只派給學員」、「只供社工跟進開的會員申請」，又指已主動聯絡服務使用者，不用居民提出申請，甚至有機構指可安排即時入會，成為會員便可領取。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201011/bkn-20201011135551499-1011_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201011%2Fbkn-20201011135551499-1011_00822_001.html&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=a008c251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201011/bkn-20201011135551499-1011_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d2d7eafac3360426f4aa5a234c8791cfdbc06d16","tid":2238920,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"NGO<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c55286a4153dbf697e60274508c452438b6783","tid":2238920,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"NGO告急 】恆常捐款人停止捐款，令社福機構收入減少 政府應提供支援措施<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gchgdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gchgdS</a>"},{"pid":"cd407336997ae577d905883f97e07d763af3bb2e","tid":2238920,"uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjfGDdn.gif\" data-thumbnail-